[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あれがブラオール名物のアイス屋で、\nそれからこっちが名所の占い通り……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00277",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "目をキラキラさせちゃって。\n私もアイス屋はちょっと気になるけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00278",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "話に聞いているのと、実際に見るのとでは大違い。\nこれが、本当のブラオール……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00279",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ふふっ……アルビーナも\n元気が戻ってきてよかった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00280",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あー、ここ最近、色々あったものね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00281",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "占いオババ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ちょっと、そこのお嬢ちゃん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_700_036_00282",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ん？　私？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00283",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "占いオババ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "違う。その隣の子じゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_700_036_00284",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、は、はい、なんでしょうか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00285",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あっ、気を付けて。占い広場では勝手に占って\n代金を要求する占い師がいるって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00286",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "占いオババ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "失礼な、これはタダじゃよ！\nお主、災難の相が出ておるぞよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_700_036_00287",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "災難の相、ですか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00288",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "占いオババ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "さらには驚きの出会いが待っておるじゃろうが、\n決して呑まれてはいけぬぞよ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_700_036_00289",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、ありがとうございます……\nって、行っちゃった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00290",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "なんだったんだろ、今の……\nとりあえずぼったくられはしなかったけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00291",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "彼女はこの占い通り一の占い師。\n人呼んでブラオールのママだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00292",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "アルビーナたち、声がする方へ振り返る",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "え？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00293",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "しかしママはかなりの気分屋で、気が乗らないときは\nいくら金を積んでも占ってくれないというのに珍しいね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00294",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "珍しいのはその格好なんですけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00295",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ええと……ブラオールにはお詳しいんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00296",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうだね。俺のシマと言っても過言じゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00297",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "絶対過言でしょ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00298",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……賞金稼ぎのジョゼといえば\nここらじゃ本当に有名なんだけどなあ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00299",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それを知らないって……\nいったいどこから来た御仁たち？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00300",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ノーヴァ神聖国。田舎者で悪ぅござんした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00301",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、あそこか……あの国の教えはどうにも苦手だよ。\n行きすぎているというか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00302",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "まぁそれには同意っすね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00303",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……おや？　そこの小粋な姉さん、\n前に会ったことない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00304",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "また随分古臭いナンパの手口だねぇ。\nでもまあ、そうさね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00305",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "昔はここらの島を巡ったこともあったから、\nそん時にすれ違ったりでもしたのかもしれないね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00306",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうかい。こんな強そうな人忘れそうに\nないんだけど。ところで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00307",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そこに隠れているのもあんたらのお仲間かい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00308",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あ、あはは……バレちゃった。鋭いね、おじさん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00309",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おじさん！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00310",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "キューン……！\nお前さん、つけてきてたのかい！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00311",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "どうやら敵じゃないようだね。とんだお節介か。\nじゃあな、ブラオールを楽しんでくれ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00312",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あっ……行っちゃいました。\nなんだかちょっと傷ついていたような",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00313",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あの、イェルカ姉貴と話したいんだ。\nここじゃなんだから……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00314",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "……分かった、場所を移して聞こうじゃないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00315",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "姉貴……お願いだから、マスターの命令に\n従って……この人たちからいったん離れよう？　ね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00316",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "キューン……お前さんは優しいから\nわざわざ説得しに来てくれた――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00317",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ってわけじゃなさそうだね。\n何か事情があるようだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00318",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……ごめんなさい。\nじゃなきゃ、私は……っ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00319",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "力ずくでも、姉貴を連れ帰らなくちゃ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00320",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "力ずくってのは、粋じゃないねぇ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00321",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]